 Tourist Safety Monitoring System
1. Introduction

The Tourist Safety Monitoring System is a smart system developed to ensure the safety of tourists while traveling. It helps monitor tourist locations and allows them to send emergency alerts when they face dangerous situations. The system helps authorities or emergency services respond quickly and provide assistance.

2. Working Model

The working process of the system includes the following steps:

Tourists register in the system through a mobile app or website.

The system tracks the tourist's location using GPS.

If a tourist faces danger, they can press an emergency alert button.

The alert message and location are sent to authorities or emergency contacts.

Authorities monitor the situation and provide immediate help.
3. AI Used

The system can use Artificial Intelligence for improving safety:

Location Prediction AI – Predicts risky areas for tourists.

Facial Recognition AI – Identifies missing persons.

Chatbot AI – Provides tourist guidance and safety information.

Anomaly Detection AI – Detects unusual activities in tourist areas.

